snippet.textDisplay: This song is beyond beautiful, the lyrics are so magical, the way they are uttered, and the depth that's there in them, especially Jaffer's ending lyrics are everything.. This song is so so relatable in this era of today due to its amazing and meaningful lyrics :), listening it on repeat to be reminded to understand the things before assuming it or taking bigger steps :) ..  Cannot thank Coke Studio for bringing this amazing melody to us, to me this is the best song of this season <3

snippet.textDisplay: This is quality music with deep and inspirational lyrics. The things i like about these lyrics: this is a story of every individual who has embarked on the journey of finding himself in order to find the truth. A person who is trying to comprehend the complexities of life in order to clear his consciousness and attain peace. The best thing about this song is the intricacy and accuracy with which emotions have been translated into music 🎵
